<section class="header">
    <hgroup>
        <h1>Varadkar wants AstraZeneca used to vaccinate young people</h1>
                            <h2> Policy change could help slow spread of Delta variant but will take at least two weeks
            </h2>
            </hgroup>
    





                
<div class="article-top-area">
                    <div class="time-metadata ">
            <time title="Wed, Jun 23, 2021, 13:30 (IST)">about 9 hours ago</time>
    </div>
                                                                <div class="article-metadata ">
                            
<div class="author">
    
